elop the venue, and make sure to create a unique atmosphere. Earn more likes to unlock more music tracks and customize your nightspot.\n\nKey features\n- Cream Soda tracks as game levels. Objects in the club react to the beat, turning the game into a music video. \n- Nightclub as the game world. Purchase and place disco balls, speakers, projectors, poufs, and other furnishings.\n- Patron is the law. Some want to dance, some want to eat, and others come to socialize. Your task is to cater to everyone\u2019s needs.\n- Interact with Cream Soda band members as game characters and upgrade their DJ equipment.\n- Sync up with Cream Soda\u2019s music!\n", "short_description": "Cream Soda Club transports you into the world of EDM and parties. Play as an event manager: furnish the club and throw parties with Cream Soda."}]}, "developer_name": "Cream Soda Club Team", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://itseven-studio.com/privacy_policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Cream Soda Club Team", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://itseven-studio.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "939033889924114"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "ru"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "208993575286907"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 0, "nodes": []}, "baseline_offer": null, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": []}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_